  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766983773-UJYQ81TUIJVW9Q50U4EK/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Week 18 + 19 and yup, you guessed it. Still loving Project Life.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2b-DSC_00621-600x290.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766998825-LXH4DNVO0QDNI25D3V5R/2b-DSC_00621-600x290.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2c-DSC_0060-600x556.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766999090-PBIOB3GTDII164ZR82HK/2c-DSC_0060-600x556.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2d-DSC_00611-600x570.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766999443-D16JLCNDAYURW24IRH4I/2d-DSC_00611-600x570.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Kept it fairly simple with the documentation as I lacked photos. Happy to have collected a lot of fun mail while I was horizontal. It was a weekend of doing a whole lot of nothing (resting and healing was the number 1 priority). Phew - so glad that week's done.  Supplies: <a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/shop/heyjenrenee\">Dude thought bubble</a>, <a href=\"http://eliseblaha.typepad.com/stampshop/\">Elise Joy stamps</a>, <a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/shop/annmarielovespaper\">Ann-Marie Loves Paper stamp</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/technique-tuesday/128131-hello-routine-april-studio-ae-clear-stamp-limited-edition/%3Ffilters%3D_technique%2Btuesday_%252Fstamps\">Ali Edwards Technique Tuesday stamps</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/126973-amy-tangerine-sketchbook-clear-acrylic-stamps/%3Ffilters%3D_sketchbook%2Bstamps_%252Fstamps\">Sketchbook stamps</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/hero-arts/125238-chevron-background-cling-stamp-co-branded-with-studio-calico/%3Ffilters%3D_chevron%2Bstamp_\">Chevron background stamp</a>, paper scraps, HeyDay 6X6 paper pad, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_washi%2520tapes_/%3Fpp%3D300\">washi tapes</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2e-DSC_0066-600x305.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600767028662-O5Z9MAULYUZ1VU9K2N5D/2e-DSC_0066-600x305.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2f-DSC_0063-600x570.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600767028928-KYPM9CSPLO8P6TE80J37/2f-DSC_0063-600x570.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2g-DSC_0064-600x553.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600767029336-KWY2TGH9T0F2M1IKL49A/2g-DSC_0064-600x553.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Aah, this week was so much better in many ways. I would recommend <a href=\"http://www.terranea.com/\">Terranea Resort</a> as a great getaway for both adults and children. Perhaps it deserves a post all on it’s own soon. Supplies: <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/technique-tuesday/128131-hello-routine-april-studio-ae-clear-stamp-limited-edition/%3Ffilters%3D_technique%2Btuesday_%252Fstamps\">Ali Edwards Technique Tuesday stamps</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/126955-grass-amy-tangerine-sketchbook-journal-foam-thickers-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_sketchbook%2Bthickers_%252Fstickers\">Journal Thickers</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/126946-addis-adoration-12x12-amy-tangerine-sketchbook-paper/%3Ffilters%3D_sketchbook_\">Hearts paper</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/lawn-fawn/126010-youve-got-mail-clear-stamp-set/%3Ffilters%3D_you%2527ve%2Bgot%2Bmail%2Blawn%2Bfawn_%252Fstamps\">Lawn Fawn stamp set</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/hero-arts/125240-airmail-clear-stamp-co-branded-with-studio-calico/%3Ffilters%3D_studio%2Bcalico%2B_\">Studio Calico stamps</a> mostly from <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/last-30-days/\">Two Peas in A Bucket</a>, some from the local independent stores I visited recently.</p><p>You can see all my Project Life posts <a href=\"http://static.squarespace.com/static/54763a73e4b0d25603e00ba7/54a756aae4b0f2d6f3befd4e/54a773bfe4b0f2d6f3c1cc6d/1420260287567/project-life?format=original\">here</a>. And the <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/mn/search/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;field-keywords=project%20life&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps#/ref=nb_sb_noss_1?url=search-alias=aps\">Project Life photo pocket pages</a> are available on Amazon.</p>"
